ortant;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在美以与伊朗战争的第十一天， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/WQbyEBd9iMYLMCCZ8R_Uad6xMxL6rJ2a3wpjivMTH_kKeqZRckR24QpsR_hXxJyT6Et2QCL9aVMGEdtF6C8FMuZKmbDVK4YWWlOaYQD0abP8zeKQi6bjZqj9nZs36hTRQJnCCK2zFsID7hkpJBlkqM1oppuDUuvYrWviQJKlyPy8mD5EevQT8eT57pLDcw115g9u9UO_8z76O66SspK0Gjl4Px8G3yAIakhVieU4thDuHb8c7ZCwRAFp7TFJuEbR7pa1FYgtfTInMEaaVvk2IWymaDhGKJhuk4GtC9RIaVcpgh7gtZyi1Q7cfWW26oflexaVuRZ8maEqim59YL-EP5IJTyCq_ncv7ICSVHvnRkncLMS3z1xwFYvhLTRfV3iWN2lpfiVbkD1hrD8TeyF12k5ANoJPe02mjpyxcyKSbzFaMSaQjQ5pjvCQ1OquzJ_zZK7idwYIjTa8wLpgj35TyOLvAs6hn8GjxEQ58e6qK30TZNJDoFBw2B8BifddLzaXVGpZ-A/dpt9PV-Dg2GwvqomQzNnt-YgcOao75JU/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="白宫否认霍尔木兹护航，但保留选择余地"&gt;双方都升级了攻击，&lt;/a&gt;因为石油市场出现了新的波动，而特朗普政府继续就战争原因以及战争可能如何结束发出混杂的信息。美国官员表示，外交谈判的可能性很小，这给唐纳德·特朗普最近提出的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wafgrA9HyJQ4c8_SVkX8KvtkUHVhRBlXBaNVxhv7x0rtyqjDHV8FlZgQRYBQDuu7Syk-KbOP13DSVJ2CMCkfxylaaPaJQL5O3IHmy36Xsr__nQFnZejtAclivE_WAteFbLDTbXauO_srCuEQqRW6j00DNgrb42coIjjkNwJkG2gW4RrZPB_FokyfuzROvWIjVyMTgq74d25p_5e72zg3aGZ-iGsGF-aM0Y1ymzxZQxuU0sELwbR68g6h54YPWnGjDXETMMrP_Tzd3JPUktPWmo9M09-04Rn4k0xt92FBU_ECHAsh85_3XLypvNT-BiX_MvGkeIj_zRNzwE1v0Kxsu-fLaBq2KW-dHTO3EgtLdCoSnZp-KPrPDiLii6DjURVsDa-qrl3MmH7r8Nt65nR0Rpzrh0Yf2SNzupSOxT11_h4mWOYoJ7cT0U9_QyPM3qlWhrKobRzjEfjK4qY38DuU60L6axieevzi7aqHnkkzDRG-HUAnJsqB6sPc10Pr/zINqTA05jVrut7KZoNhZcSKJGh_l7Aya/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普言论导致美国石油收盘后交易下跌"&gt;冲突可能很快得到解决的&lt;/a&gt;建议泼了一盆冷水。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;周二，人们的注意力&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/WsE5FDb4jZH0DNpUCviYX271pZ6v1Aui8E9TGUvCP5_bqRrM5cbdnxqeUsMczApTJ-Hgp4x1pMseOm92Uknl7jQg4An8p-6_fOr57YBDPRvwj35HGdhJNjmL5873XdfWSFZ3DDDgs0h-uMUYPK_6ce1