ont-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;参议院多数党领袖约翰·图恩警告说，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普迫使共和党通过对投票法进行党派改革的努力&lt;/strong&gt;可能会导致国会事务陷入停顿，而且&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eeiFW5IdsZR_IkwGBqXXa2I8ttjoiRhQDugpE6x9eHB9PPKzPS71vhqF31aRWsoDviImaMIAprExHfxlsjLBiZLlX6nlNrrNP5N-6JuORhCMtDqmd9QopJF9Ekr9VLJ-1ZZSKEj3g44F3XftjeG-lU5OXF8cp17x0YcmnnzQNHkLiGMP7CHNSwCIdukT9LjNcoMvX7Om4kzWeMsoFiRFAq86UgeYbXltftIN-esQn4cxuhMt0BnFJmJK9ERNC5XeIlGwT-CElIhuA-6ZacFMymQpxDKlI5QU7IAi2gN8iJ5XbOE84isY33QbcuGhE1lZPHQxqKDxOVvxBlNj-UDJAU2Y_jkt6bzHlCaAFoxZvbyTcM0GIRZYHAZQPzI/H1B5xE_W_YNCBpir11yMuQv4UfbtbD7P/18" target="_blank"&gt;没有明确的成功之路&lt;/a&gt;。在对总统的另一项挑战中，一名美国法官裁定特朗普政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LyDfv5BPLPttk3KqMyJ5s32bR2YuzeEtLbLQITPgpm-dJkemsWAgWpucbGjyHwxnLkcelcVlxLjv9hrb9SH20aSZn5eEr5gNjd6VKHbaN0Afm8fEmh9WfoDGCgbZGiw8gPiBToqabyBBhOavV-9SZQvJq9o0XTzceJYI84KsgfL1ZSZiu2rq0QiCzW5HoKvXBaEafY9468mDxjcCZBuKj9eNKAdAoz28CV1WDN_KwUj9mukgoIdsLfBGnQKqvhh1xaOXIZYjcvbwmHB4T6e_ZkkP3IjLHTib2ufKtN5lO8GAVVqYUNdKZm9uFd67klr26iyrr6hYA2STLp7fAAQeg27bscSbaF0Fax7Ncs5Tp_G31pjUfpMXXBrV3Q0/4av-n7Pm5f1AvdFuV08q_NfOLRqkLePI/18" target="_blank"&gt;非法任命三名律师&lt;/a&gt;在阿丽娜·哈巴辞去新泽西州最高联邦检察官职务后接替她。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普实施移民镇压&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一年&lt;/strong&gt;后，我们几乎没有看到任何证据表明更严格的边境政策正在改善美国出生的工人的就业前景。移民紧缩&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Hp2Oux5Ov1_SRGvU5ISXgxiyuXD3fdlhq_72AASnPiCdgFZNbCF_2FFEUPdOOZveeHfsNOHBdl0LEaZiDn8bYEXCfA_oJlgeSpX6C8JJ1UvXs3pvgjxELj9jafcSc6HxyewR9MDg_pugKB0sqynY4bPOqtpdmltZsn5ujzoOHpYzbcfiBuaq-ezfS36lhblPws4l4MUSygAbQ3lctblQfUQ-obmEyJpn8rb4ynMbT0M5IOqrSsg5oWPkQOGFVoN8RvL3rN0b3CR999GOMRwy1vDRZJOrI4eH2UarLCPHiHqIh_OO15cj1NSe36E8gBvoEMEk_K3-bj4dao6ciqDH8HtkISa3jTIqHsUw6asXhuU7-_3L0xGIn_hOKU4/6x600zwde3VEvC6ZZGgC6mRFoYN2GQI3/18" target="_blank" title="工作机会"&gt;与本土出生的失业率上升&lt;/a&gt;同时发生，尽管一些企业表示填补职位空缺变