t;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;委内瑞拉初步批准了&lt;/strong&gt;一项采矿法案，政府承诺以“特朗普的速度”振兴该行业并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/r2smQWDtPMluruqoUJvIM59UZa7L2_u3reORB60jRWhBEuiySBgGFhFbtmeMgeTuI-RM9WDS_5wFLnMWTjB7hHa9aUF-Ts6wh6-iFNBFVh8YM2gnLCLbtzToSEHVWL0NKWYmTg9OEfrKsS87AqJj9h-Vy3rFi6lEepdLxld-fqgBE_s7Rec8HmCMf3qdmABUf9lgsjECIyYhY_eOF_-gX5Z_4pepaDXcdZaX6reRo22TTbag88A8moEaqdEfI59-y22wX0jADp1i_DYPmimtVrG-hD13rUudjSe6lzV0xBob8LZOjW8xDMMYoBWReNyakZKJFtxqvjXpN73AcYMSXTst2tjRpWUurmHCff8lA3ohy7FkgS1U10ROBfI/2kCU9HufzQOvOGFni57iLdopGEmiDfWX/18" target="_blank"&gt;吸引外国投资&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这是继特朗普在一月份推翻前总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗之后，委内瑞拉和美国之间经济和政治关系升温的最新迹象&lt;/strong&gt;。上周，在内政部长道格·布尔古姆访问后不久，双方同意&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mrpX8sNDPPGkwQz2d8r4g-PFb_mSnGFyE7yj1woTl9iKnJLyMsj_07R6rVQ01mWoG6IIrpk5RYz_b1X6RVsG4NXk7gzaH3vFFSHNhFUkzp6LHfI31bKlySryvgy2hZ1yC0vKu6wkdwbKiTmw1EX6E21yEOIwnjsFqQ2lnVFzCEMb__5iCKkJCF7fT4v7f-GykQpKfNeVAe2pKZkOXxJ1Y0M0Cgj3i_lzS4fm8rS3pJeOpRLsFrHFbSrGyKwjaiQqpMa1z0tjfLMdWdkzDNNS8kCwa3bXVVbsE2CXYx2vT151mjjA3v7RsBa0pSFkgGcCNaC56GN7wDHFfMRR6-g8TVJYXkEZcWm1L8Ji43lYPK2xHMcRhD7mrCCj39A/pqfGOwfCMvNGqz3eqPFZ9OHsrW_lOUtC/18" target="_blank"&gt;恢复外交关系&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;采矿法案&lt;/strong&gt;以一月份的类似立法为基础，当时委内瑞拉立法者批准了对其长达数十年的民族主义石油政策的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/J8J0oQ_HQdeKWtBthXJ6N8aXJ9SQ4Ah6dXKUF1p4tjNHLExooGmc2uG9SctSAZzWgtXph3DC8wWDleYbvVC34-SH-OclZp4bEBQ0CxHFMVBU-MymfRxkuyiVAB2_AmA9VUt6l4ZS49xFUpuz3GBcsAFhzq0bSekxrTUXqDyidg05EFqrMiO5fwjR8rRzEgK47ZOn9imXJKdtC4IewaPYWghij5bZc0rz_YE5uL4uSfV-IDUbQSC3S_3H4S8-larYYKZFz3D5hlLq5QJarJkRmLSAgRrEhCeicPYmt8Z2qhZI25fuXMm-lc-jaQt6qOrFWrKtx-bO5buoysq3Q9eVSgcfG0IjDMkkaJChdYBTGSEX3-8MhGH